OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy day with outbreaks of
OL,6,Frain some of which will be heavy at
OL,7,Ftimes, but there should be a few drier
OL,8,Finterludes too, especially later.
OL,9,
OL,10,CTonight:FA cloudy evening and night
OL,11,Fwith spells of showery rain. Rain will
OL,12,Fbe locally heavy at first, but
OL,13,Fbecoming somewhat drier for a period
OL,14,Fafter midnight.
OL,15,
OL,16,CTuesday:FPartly cloudy with showers
OL,17,Fdeveloping, some heavy and perhaps
OL,18,Fmerging into longer spells of rain,
OL,19,Fwith a risk of thunder.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
